    "title": "Initializing a new database with -txindex=1 set asks for reindex",
    "body": "When the client is started without database, but with txindex=1 set, it exits, telling that you need to reindex to change the value of that flag.\n\nThat warning shouldn't need to be shown when initializing a fresh database.\n\nCaused by #2648, I assume.\n",
